snippet.title: Those Who Came: Healing Solarus PVP GAMEPLAY Showcase
snippet.description:
Enjoy and observe the match between these two players of Those Who Came: Healing Solarus in its PVP Mode. Who will win? 

Those Who Came: Healing Solarus is the first title of Spanish indie developer Rolldbox Games. This sci-fi title where healing and cooperation are key to success on the surface of a hostile planet is now available on Steam 🌌👉🔗https://bit.ly/twchs2 

See you in space!
